snippet: Santonio Holmes left Sunday’s game with what the Jets called a foot injury, the severity of which isn’t yet certain for a team that’s in short supply of playmakers of his caliber.
abstract: New York Jets wide receiver Santonio Holmes injuries his left leg during team's loss to the San Francisco 49ers, another crucial blow to a team already in short supply of high-caliber playmakers.
lead_paragraph: Santonio Holmes left Sunday’s game with what the Jets called a foot injury, the severity of which isn’t yet certain for a team that’s in short supply of playmakers of his caliber.

headline.seo: Injury to Santonio Holmes May Limit Jets Further
headline.main: More Cause for Worry: An Injury to Holmes
